prompts.title: Pose strass dentaire
prompts.content: Generate a hyper-realistic fashion photo shot from a low angle or dramatic close-up, focusing on a woman’s mouth as she shows off her teeth by pulling her lips apart. Fingers are adorned with edgy rings and nail art. Skin texture, lip gloss, and natural lighting details must be sharp. The model expresses bold attitude — rebellious, playful, or fierce. No dental gems or modifications on teeth.
